comments.body:
From [StyleCopAnalyzers v1.2.0-beta.354](https://github.com/DotNetAnalyzers/StyleCopAnalyzers/releases/tag/1.2.0-beta.354), there is a configuration option `layoutRules.allowDoWhileOnClosingBrace` in `stylecop.json` to allow the following:

```
} while (false);
```

See: https://github.com/DotNetAnalyzers/StyleCopAnalyzers/pull/3196
